# DB Meter

```
$ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-dbmeter
$ npm install --save @ionic-native/db-meter
```

## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/db-meter/)

Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/akofman/cordova-plugin-dbmeter](https://github.com/akofman/cordova-plugin-dbmeter)

This plugin defines a global DBMeter object, which permits to get the decibel values from the microphone.

## Supported platforms
- Android
- iOS



